    {
      "id": "ApMx9cka4TT7kA5TzHhEd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1131.997980048392,
      "y": 4070.9236575132745,
      "width": 886.9495178160778,
      "height": 55.65697360719165,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0D",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 837647867,
      "version": 567,
      "versionNonce": 1551339070,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777374734427,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "子代理机制将复杂任务“模块化”，通过隔离上下文、强化专业性、限制权限和开启并行，极\n大地提升了 Claude Code 处理复杂软件工程问题的效率和准确度。",
      "fontSize": 22.26278944287666,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "子代理机制将复杂任务“模块化”，通过隔离上下文、强化专业性、限制权限和开启并行，极大地提升了 Claude Code 处理复杂软件工程问题的效率和准确度。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WNcLeT569SMpjflboFGiK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -916.943675577678,
      "y": 3533.543499703247,
      "width": 609.6721576903147,
      "height": 58.985310767320556,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1882075989,
      "version": 514,
      "versionNonce": 1697060478,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777374734427,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "每个子代理拥有独立的上下文\n子代理处理具体任务时，主代理的上下文窗口能保持“干净”",
      "fontSize": 23.594124306928226,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "每个子代理拥有独立的上下文\n子代理处理具体任务时，主代理的上下文窗口能保持“干净”",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mCZKWi2ypmVjNblpyL7pl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -910.8431766951965,
      "y": 3668.436141972532,
      "width": 431.7441552970947,
      "height": 58.985310767320556,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 754343957,
      "version": 548,
      "versionNonce": 2000393918,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777374734427,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为不同的子代理设定更专注的系统提示词\n术业有专攻",
      "fontSize": 23.594124306928226,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为不同的子代理设定更专注的系统提示词\n术业有专攻",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
